OL,5, An e-bike rider was pulled over by     
OL,6, police while cycling along the M25.    
OL,8,FPolice stopped the rider on the        
OL,9,Fmotorway hard shoulder at Potters Bar  
OL,10,Fin Hertfordshire on Sunday.            
OL,12,FNot only is it illegal to ride one on a
OL,13,Fmotorway, but the bicycle itself was   
OL,14,Falso illegal on any UK road because of 
OL,15,Fits high power, officers said.         
OL,17,FIts higher speed meant the e-bike fell 
OL,18,F"outside of (the) regulations and      
OL,19,Fcannot be ridden on our roads", said   
OL,20,Fpolice, who seized it.                 
